name: Alton Beach Babies' shoes
description:
Pair, black sports velcro strapped children’s shoes
Melbourne, Australia
15 January 2019

Young Tyler or Maddox or Kyle or whatever the millennials are calling their kids nowadays must be fraught with regret somewhere in Melbourne.

-----

The Lost Shoe Project brings together participants from around the world, in a performance piece documented in close-to-real-time as a sequence of photographic images of lost or abandoned shoes. The Collector presents this first array of his most loved images.
